    "Notably, even when the algorithm fails to simulate 3D structures, ReaMVP's sequence encoder can still effectively predict chemical reaction yields.ReaMVP stands out from the state-of-the-art methods with its exceptional performance in out-of-sample scenarios, demonstrating its potential in predicting chemical reaction yields involving unseen additives or ligands.",
    "Additionally, the model can be extended to other prediction tasks related to chemical reaction outcomes.",
